io":0.0,"revenue":24795199488.0,"revenue_per_share":180.998,"revenue_growth":0.034,"ebitda":4057825024.0,"ebitda_margins":0.16364999,"gross_margins":0.42574,"operating_margins":0.13549,"profit_margins":0.09981,"net_income":2474800128.0,"total_cash":3363800064.0,"total_cash_per_share":24.35,"total_debt":644200000.0,"debt_to_equity":2.462,"enterprise_value":79021588480.0,"enterprise_to_ebitda":19.474,"enterprise_to_revenue":3.187,"earnings_growth":-0.146,"shares_outstanding":136989230.0,"float_shares":23035902.0,"held_pct_insiders":0.83325,"held_pct_institutions":0.09491,"fifty_two_week_high":760.0,"fifty_two_week_low":533.25,"fifty_day_average":573.87,"two_hundred_day_avg":604.5607,"target_high_price":800.0,"target_low_price":745.0,"target_mean_price":761.25,"recommendation":"none","num_analyst_opinions":4,"all_time_high":760.0,"all_time_low":533.25,"long_business_summary":"Orkla India Limited operates as a food company, manufactures and sells spices and convenience foods in India and internationally. It offers sambar, chicken, puliogare, rasam, and meat blended spice masala; and chilli, kashmiri chilli, turmeric, coriander, and cumin pure spices. The company also provides ready-to-cook, such as breakfast, sweet, and badam milk beverage mixes; ready-to-eat, includes paneer butter masala, dal makhani, and chana masala, as well as various rice dishes such as veg pulao and tomato rice; vermicelli and macaroni; badam drink and coffee beverages, pickles, ginger garlic paste, malabar parotas, cooking aids, pulses, rice, coconut milk, desserts, and other confectionery items. It sells its products through e-commerce websites and commerce platform under the MTR, Eastern, Rasoi Magic, Wok N Roll, and Laban brand names. The company was formerly known as MTR Foods Private Limited. The company was founded in 1924 and is based in Bengaluru, India. Orkla India Limited is a subsidiary of Orkla Asia Pacific Pte. Ltd."}}